quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,“Kodi sitidachiphanule chifuwa chako (pokupatsa chiongoko ndi chikhulupiliro ndi nzeru zambiri)
  94,2,“Ndipo takuchotsera mtolo wako (pa ntchito yolalikira pokuthandiza ndi kukufewetsera zinthu zako)
  94,3,“Mtolo umene udalemetsa msana wako
  94,4,“Ndipo takukweza kutchulidwa kwako
  94,5,“Ndipo ndithu pali chovuta palinso zabwino (Zambiri)
  94,6,“Ndithu pali chovuta palinso zabwino (zambiri)
  94,7,"“Basi, ukamaliza ntchito (yolalikira ndi Jihâd) limbikira kupemphera"
  94,8,“Ndipo khala wolakalaka (zabwino zomwe zili) kwa Mbuye wako
  95,1,“Ndikulumbilira mitengo ya Mkuyu ndi Zitona (pansi pa mitengo imeneyi Ibrahim ndi Nuh (Nowa) adapeza uneneri
  95,2,“Ndi phiri la Sinai (pamene Allah adamulankhulira Mûsa)
  95,3,"“Ndiponso mzinda uwu (wolemekezeka) wamtendere; (Makka, womwe adapatsiridwa uneneri Muhammad) (s.a.w)"
  95,4,"“Palibe chikaiko, tamulenga munthu mkalengedwe kabwino, kolingana (ndipo ali ndi mbiri zabwino)"
  95,5,“Pambuyo pake tamubwezera pansi kumposa wa pansi
  95,6,"“Kupatula amene akhulupirira ndikumachita zabwino, adzakhala nawo iwo malipiro osatha"
  95,7,“Tsono nchiyani chakuchititsa kuti ukanire kuuka ndi malipiro pambuyo (poona mphamvu zathu pa chilichonse)
  95,8,“Kodi Allah si Muweruzi wa nzeru kuposa aweruzi onse
  96,1,"“Werenga! (Iwe Mneneri (s.a.w), zomwe zikuvumbulutsidwa) mdzina la Mbuye wako Yemwe adalenga (zolengedwa zonse)"
  96,2,“Adalenga munthu kuchokera ku magazi owundana
  96,3,“Werenga! Ndipo Mbuye wako ndi Wopereka kwambiri
  96,4,“Yemwe waphunzitsa (munthu kulemba) ndi cholembera
  96,5,“Waphunzitsa munthu zinthu (zambiri) zomwe (iye) sadali kuzidziwa
  96,6,“Zoona ndithu koma munthu akupyola malire (podzikweza)
  96,7,“Chifukwa chodziona kuti walemera
  96,8,"“Palibe chikaiko, (iwe Mneneri (s.a.w) kobwerera (onse) nkwa Mbuye wako basi; (adzawaukitsa)"
  96,9,“Kodi wamuona yemwe akuletsa
  96,10,“Kapolo (wa Allah) akamapemphera
  96,11,“Tandiuza ngati ali pachiongoko
  96,12,“Kapena kuti akulamulira zoopa Allah
  96,13,“Tandiuza (za woletsayo) ngati akutsutsa (zimene wadza nazo Mneneri) ndikunyoza (chikhulupiliro ndi ntchito yabwino)
  96,14,“Kodi sakudziwa kuti Allah akuona (machitidwe ake. Ndipo adzamlipira)
  96,15,“Ayi ndithu ngati sasiya timukoka tsitsi lapatsumba (tiligwira mwamphamvu tsumba lake ndikukamponya ku Moto)
  96,16,“Tsumba labodza (ndiponso) lamachimo
  96,17,"“Basi aliitane gulu lakelo, (la amene amakhala nawo pabwalo kuti amthandize pano pa dziko kapena tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  96,18,“Nafe tiitana azabaniya (angelo a ku Moto)
  96,19,"“Ayi ndithu usamumvere (pa zimene akukuletsazo); koma gwetsa nkhope yako pansi, ndipo dziyandikitse kwa Mbuye wako"
  97,1,“Ndithu taivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wa Qadr (usiku wolemekezeka)
  97,2,“Ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za usiku wolemekezekawu
  97,3,“Usiku olemekezekawu uli wabwino kuposa miyezi chikwi chimodzi ( yomwe mulibe Laila-tul-Qadr)
  97,4,“Amatsika angelo ndi Jiburil mmenemo mwa chilolezo cha Mbuye wawo kudzalongosola chinthu chilichonse
  97,5,“Mtendere usiku umenewo! (Palibe mavuto ndi zoipa) mpaka m’bandakucha
  98,1,“Amene adakanira (Allah ndi Mthenga Wake) mwa omwe adapatsidwa buku ndi opembedza mafano sadali olekana (ndi umbuli wawo ndi kusalabadira kwawo choona) mpaka pomwe chidawadzera chisonyezo choonekera poyera
  98,2,“(Yemwe ndi) Mtumiki wochokera kwa Allah akuwawerengera makalata oyeretsedwa (ku zonama)
  98,3,“Omwe mkati mwake muli malamulo oongoka (ofotokoza za choona)
  98,4,“Sadalekane omwe adapatsidwa mabuku mpaka pomwe chidawafikira chisonyezo (chosonyeza kuti Muhammad (s.a.w) ndi mthenga wa Allah yemwe adalonjezedwa mmabuku awo
  98,5,“Ndipo sadalamulidwe (china) koma kuti ampembedze Allah (Mmodzi yekha) ndikuyeretsa chipembedzo chake popendekera ku choona (ndi kusiya njira zonama) ndi kuti asunge Swala ndiponso apereke chopereka (cha pachuma chawo); chimenecho (ndicho) chipembedzo choongoka
  98,6,“Ndithu amene sadakhulupirire (Mneneri) (s.a.w) pakati pa anthu a mabuku ndi opembedza mafano adzalowetsedwa ku Jahannam ndikukhala m’menemo nthawi yaitali; iwowo ndiwo zolengedwa zoipa
  98,7,"“Ndithu amene akhulupirira (mwa Allah ndi Mthenga Wake) ndikumachita zabwino, iwo ndiwo zolengedwa zabwino"
  98,8,"“Malipiro awo kwa Mbuye wawo, ndi minda yamuyaya momwe ikuyenda pansi pake mitsinje; adzakhala m’menemo muyaya. Allah adzawayanja nawonso adzamuyanja (chifukwa cha zomwe adzawapatse); zimenezo ndi za yemwe awope Mbuye wake (Allah)"
  99,1,“Likadzagwedezedwa dziko lapansi kugwedezeka kwake kwamphamvu
  99,2,"“Ndipo nthaka idzatulutsa mitolo yake (zinthu zomwe zidali mkati mwake, monga akufa ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali)"
  99,3,"“Ndipo munthu adzanena (mwa mantha, ndikudabwa nthawi imeneyo). Ha! Yatani nthaka, (kodi Qiyâma yafika)"
  99,4,"“Tsiku limenelo idzanena nkhani zake zonse, (zabwino kapena zoipa)"
  99,5,“Pakuti Mbuye wako adzailamula kutero (kuti igwedezeke ndikunena zimene zinkachitika pamwamba pake)
  99,6,“Tsiku limenelo anthu adzachoka (m’manda) ali m’magulu obalalika kuti akasonyezedwe ntchito zawo (ndikudziwa chiwerengero chawo chimene chili kwa Allah)
  99,7,"“Choncho, amene angachite chabwino cholemera ngati kanjere kakang’ono, adzaona malipiro ake"
  99,8,"“Ndipo amene angachite choipa cholemera ngati kanjere kakang’ono, adzaona malipiro ake. (Allah sachitira chinyengo aliyense)"
  100,1,“Ndikulumbilira akavalo othamanga ali ndi phuma
  100,2,“Ndi otulutsa moto ku zikhotwa (pomenyetsa miyendo m’miyala)
  100,3,“Ndi othira nkhondo adani mmawa (dzuwa lisadatuluke)
  100,4,“Ndi kuulutsa fumbi lambiri (kwa adani) nthawi imeneyo
  100,5,“Ndikulowelera mkatikati mwa adani
  100,6,"“Ndithu munthu ali wokanira Mbuye wake, (sathokoza Allah pa zimene amdalitsa nazo)"
  100,7,“Ndithudi iye pa zimenezi ndi mboni (yodzichitira yekha kupyolera mzochitachita zake)
  100,8,“Ndipo ndithu iye ndiwokonda chuma kwambiri (ndiponso ngwamsulizo)